<br>
Well I will assume you are a real, honest to goodness, bona-fide new player.  Your somewhat of a rarity these days, but we are glad to have ya aboard.<br>
<br>
The spell Summon: Orb is indeed a level 46 spell and is the result of the Magician Epic quest.  The spell summons a hand held item that has a right click effect of Manefest Elements, commonly known as the &quot;Epic Pet&quot;.  This pet was <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>the</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> pet prior to the release of PoP as none of the 50+ pets compared to it in all but the rarest of situations.<br>
<br>
Many have spent more than a real life year working on the quest and still not completed it.  I was very fortunate to complete it myself.  If you choose to do so go into it expecting not to complete it and suprise yourself if you do. <p><hr>
